 deeper look at an important decade in the development of Vattimo's thought.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 4aPhilosophy : Continental Philosophy. 4aPhilosophy : Heidegger. 4aPhilosophy : Hermeneutics. 4aPhilosophy : Philosophy. 7aPHILOSOPHY / General.2bisacsh1 aCarravetta, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCarravetta, Peter, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143847383340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438473833423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438473833/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles